# 📈 Stock Price Prediction

## 🔹 Description
This project predicts stock prices using Machine Learning techniques.

## 🔹 Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Flask (if app.py is used)

## 🔹 Features
- Data preprocessing
- Model training
- Stock price prediction
- Web interface (if Flask)

## 🔹 Project Structure
- app.py → Main application
- STOCKPREDICTIONAPP.py → Model logic
- templates/ → HTML files
- static/ → CSS/JS files

## 🔹 How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run application:
   python app.py

